Package energy.usef.agr.workflow.nonudi.initialize

Workflow classes for Non-UDI initialization of the Aggregator.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgrInitializeNonUdiClustersParameter
    Class which contains the enumerations of the workflow parameters.
    AgrNonUdiInitializeCoordinator
    This coordinator will initialize the non-udi clusters, e.g.
    AgrNonUdiInitializeEvent
    This event will trigger the AgrNonUdiInitializeCoordinator.
    AgrNonUdiInitializeEventTrigger
    Timed trigger to fire AgrNonUdiInitializeEvent.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AgrInitializeNonUdiClustersParameter.IN
    The ingoing parameters for the initialize non-udi cluster PBC.
